{"tid":1809703,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"cheap講香港畸形的選舉制度","createTime":"2020-01-03T09:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T10:24:59.000Z","uid":239674,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf5ff172ac4976fa225d153933dc5967384c308","tid":1809703,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"節錄重點：<br />\n香港每年都會有五萬名，來自中國的新移民<br />\n逐漸的這些人可以左右香港的選舉<br />\n中國移民平常用百度，微信與微博<br />\n看的聽的用的都來自中國<br />\n情理上他們支持北京政府<br />\n又不太受香港主流民意影響<br />\n所以北京靠這種灌票戰術<br />\n就算幾年之後給你真普選好了<br />\n他也可以掌握香港政局<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6ocWCBcOJw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6ocWCBcOJw8&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7AogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=91456396\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6ocWCBcOJw8</a>"},{"pid":"8c8a008616471e91521ce2ca952aa7aa8285ecd6","tid":1809703,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"之前時事台某post有人提出新移民可以同化<br />\n我其實100%唔同意<br />\n只係未諗到個point去駁<br />\n但cheap呢條片100%講緊我所諗既野"},{"pid":"01bae4d318f4e4270b5e0a0b12c857db92997383","tid":1809703,"uid":239674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:48:08.000Z","msg":"出街食飯留意吓講普通話既新移民<br />\n最多話佢地會用whatsapp為左工作<br />\n但平時圍爐用既都係wechat<br />\n接收資訊既都係微博<br />\n你話到時投票佢既價值觀係點?<br />\n<br />\n今次區選嬴左只係證明香港人肯走出黎<br />\n唔好輕敵蝗蟲大軍"},{"pid":"472c9e323d43e40038c4410c660bf100f082eb6a","tid":1809703,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a72e122feccaf8fc9d4108ba5d7fe8016182287","tid":1809703,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c8a008616471e91521ce2ca952aa7aa8285ecd6","tid":1809703,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"之前時事台某post有人提出新移民可以同化<br />\n我其實100%唔同意<br />\n只係未諗到個point去駁<br />\n但cheap呢條片100%講緊我所諗既野"},"citedBy":1,"reply